title: #74 - FouseyTube Meltdown & RIP DaddyOFive
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast Ethan examines the "FouseyCon" controversy, the return and ban of DaddyOFive, and pays tribute to Hila's father, who unfortunately passed away this week. Rest in peace Yochanan Hakmon (1950-2018)
